'''Glareshades''', also known as '''glowshades''',<ref name="WHSV">''[[Wretched Hives of Scum & Villainy]]''</ref> '''sunglasses''', '''dark visors''', or '''sunshades''',<ref name="FBS">''[[Flashpoint! Brak Sector]]''</ref> were a piece of eyewear used either to protect one's eyes from direct exposure to sunlight or just as a nod to fashion. [[Wing Commander/Legends|Wing Commander]] [[Diblen Harleys]] of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] was known to wear glareshades as an informal part of his uniform.

